{"tid":1975130,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"一路唔封關嘅真正原因係每日150人？","createTime":"2020-04-16T10:21:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-16T10:45:41.000Z","uid":116069,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8b669b1b254d51defa7eb85fb704350727354677","tid":1975130,"uid":116069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T10:21:27.000Z","msg":"1982年，港英政府與中國政府達成協議，議定由內地來港定居者須持內地政府簽發的單程證，配額為每日75個。<br />\n1993年，單程證配額由每日75人增至每日105人。<br />\n1995年，單程證配額再由每日105人增至如今每日150人。<br />\n<br />\n柒婆一路唔封大陸關嘅原因會唔會係因為新移民政策？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可唔可以推到議員或者記者問到佢答<br />\n而家有冇停到每日150人配額，如果停左嘅係幾時停嘅？<br />\n係停配額定暫時停過境定兩樣都冇停<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c60400437fce68188ed7dc3761a99d27b41e3a2d","tid":1975130,"uid":173326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T10:22:28.000Z","msg":"當然冇停150<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33b311dd965f9892ab52a89566b0ad2cf903a40b","tid":1975130,"uid":116069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c60400437fce68188ed7dc3761a99d27b41e3a2d","tid":1975130,"uid":173326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T10:22:28.000Z","msg":"當然冇停150<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T10:23:54.000Z","msg":"都估到 <br />\n如果冇停又冇過境 <br />\n儲埋儲埋幾個月半年<br />\n遲下咪幾萬幾萬咁嚟"},{"pid":"cd202410412576de4a5738852fe9c4892d314d84","tid":1975130,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T10:25:51.000Z","msg":"講明就侵啦，香港人係二等公民呀，唔會理你生死"},{"pid":"e3f4c78234ca6b62f87f94338791098d41d2c764","tid":1975130,"uid":194326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T10:25:58.000Z","msg":"港男北上搵女朋友都唔少啦"},{"pid":"dfa71387e39137b6fbb10a0fb071eb669546938c","tid":1975130,"uid":66798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T10:26:41.000Z","msg